---
description: Database, SQL, migrations, Prisma (scoped)
globs:
  - "**/*.sql"
  - "**/*migration*"
  - "**/*migrations*"
  - "**/db/**/*"
  - "**/database/**/*"
  - "**/prisma/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Database / SQL

- Parameterized queries; migrations for schema changes; no ad hoc production mutation.
- Explicit constraints and indexes when justified; avoid unbounded reads; prefer pagination.
- Preserve transactional correctness and N+1 awareness where relevant.
